Графика в R

t = seq(0, 4, 0.01)
signal = sin(2*pi*t)
signal2 = sin(8*pi*t)

plot(t, signal, col="red", cex=I(0.4), lwd=I(0.5), pch=19, type="o")
lines(t, signal2, col = "blue", cex=I(0.6), lwd=I(.8), pch=20, type="o")
title(main="Базовая графика в R")
